In this blog, we'll delve into why this workshop is a game-changer for the utility sector.","/images/news/utility2.jpeg","Workshop, Nov 15, 08:30 am PST.","2023-Oct-03","OMA SpecWorks",60,[65],"workshop",{"type":11,"children":67},[68,72],{"type":14,"tag":15,"props":69,"children":70},{},[71],{"type":25,"value":58},{"type":14,"tag":15,"props":73,"children":74},{},[75,77,88],{"type":25,"value":76},"To register for this event, please fill out the ",{"type":14,"tag":28,"props":78,"children":81},{"href":79,"rel":80},"https://community.openmobilealliance.org/unlocking-utility-benefits-with-lwm2m-2",[40],[82],{"type":14,"tag":83,"props":84,"children":85},"strong",{},[86],{"type":25,"value":87},"CLOSED",{"type":25,"value":89},".",{"type":11,"children":91,"toc":195},[92,96,109,119,129,139,149,159,169,174,176,180,182,191,192],{"type":14,"tag":15,"props":93,"children":94},{},[95],{"type":25,"value":58},{"type":14,"tag":15,"props":97,"children":98},{},[99,100,108],{"type":25,"value":76},{"type":14,"tag":28,"props":101,"children":103},{"href":79,"rel":102},[40],[104],{"type":14,"tag":83,"props":105,"children":106},{},[107],{"type":25,"value":87},{"type":25,"value":89},{"type":14,"tag":15,"props":110,"children":111},{},[112,117],{"type":14,"tag":83,"props":113,"children":114},{},[115],{"type":25,"value":116},"Adoption: Bringing LwM2M to the Forefront",{"type":25,"value":118},"\nOne of the primary goals of the OMASpeWorks Workshop is to promote the adoption and understanding of the LwM2M protocol in the utility industry. LwM2M is a robust protocol with the potential to revolutionize utility operations, yet it remains relatively unknown in the sector. The workshop aims to shed light on its capabilities and address utility-specific challenges.",{"type":14,"tag":15,"props":120,"children":121},{},[122,127],{"type":14,"tag":83,"props":123,"children":124},{},[125],{"type":25,"value":126},"Relevance: Tailoring Solutions to Utility Needs",{"type":25,"value":128},"\nThe utility industry has unique requirements, from managing diverse device ecosystems to ensuring security and optimizing operational efficiency. The OMASpeWorks Workshop aims to demonstrate the relevance of LwM2M to these specific needs. Through real-world examples and tailored use cases, we showcase how LwM2M is not a one-size-fits-all solution but a precise answer to the industry's demands.",{"type":14,"tag":15,"props":130,"children":131},{},[132,137],{"type":14,"tag":83,"props":133,"children":134},{},[135],{"type":25,"value":136},"Benefits: The Power of LwM2M Unleashed",{"type":25,"value":138},"\nOur workshop features two white papers: \"Unlocking Utility Benefits\" and \"Unlocking Utilities Savings.\" These papers highlight the specific advantages utilities can gain from adopting LwM2M. \"Unlocking Utility Benefits\" explores how LwM2M streamlines field area management operations, while \"Unlocking Utilities Savings\" delves into potential cost savings and efficiency improvements in meter management. These papers make a compelling case for LwM2M implementation.",{"type":14,"tag":15,"props":140,"children":141},{},[142,147],{"type":14,"tag":83,"props":143,"children":144},{},[145],{"type":25,"value":146},"Standards: Driving Industry-Wide Progress",{"type":25,"value":148},"\nOMA, founded in 2002, is committed to developing and promoting open, industry-wide standards. The OMASpeWorks Workshop aligns perfectly with this mission by showcasing how LwM2M can be applied in the utility sector. By encouraging the adoption of standardized protocols like LwM2M, OMA fosters interoperability and innovation across the industry.",{"type":14,"tag":15,"props":150,"children":151},{},[152,157],{"type":14,"tag":83,"props":153,"children":154},{},[155],{"type":25,"value":156},"Decision-Making: Informed Choices for Utilities",{"type":25,"value":158},"\nUtilities often face critical decisions regarding the adoption of new technologies and protocols. Our workshop provides valuable resources that offer in-depth information, use cases, and rationale for choosing LwM2M. These resources assist utilities in evaluating the protocol's suitability for their specific needs, enabling them to make informed decisions about implementation.",{"type":14,"tag":15,"props":160,"children":161},{},[162,167],{"type":14,"tag":83,"props":163,"children":164},{},[165],{"type":25,"value":166},"Stakeholders: Fostering Collaboration",{"type":25,"value":168},"\nThe OMASpeWorks Workshop isn't just about utilities; it's about bringing together various stakeholders within the utility industry. This includes utility companies, technology providers, and regulatory bodies. By presenting a clear and compelling case for LwM2M adoption, our workshop facilitates discussions and collaborations aimed at advancing utility management practices.",{"type":14,"tag":15,"props":170,"children":171},{},[172],{"type":25,"value":173},"In conclusion, the OMASpeWorks Workshop is a game-changer for the utility industry. Through informative white papers, real-world examples, and a commitment to industry-wide standards, we aim to drive LwM2M adoption, helping utilities unlock efficiency, save costs, and innovate in their operations. Join us on this journey of transformation and be part of the future of utility management. Together, we can unlock the full potential of LwM2M!",{"type":25,"value":175},"\n ",{"type":14,"tag":177,"props":178,"children":179},"br",{},[],{"type":25,"value":181},"\n      ",{"type":14,"tag":183,"props":184,"children":185},"button",{},[186,190],{"type":14,"tag":28,"props":187,"children":188},{"href":79},[189],{"type":25,"value":87},{"type":25,"value":181},{"type":25,"value":175},{"type":14,"tag":177,"props":193,"children":194},{},[],{"title":5,"searchDepth":47,"depth":47,"links":196},[],"content:5.news:articles:2023-10-03-outreach-utility-november.md","5.news/articles/2023-10-03-outreach-utility-november.md",[200],{"_path":4,"_dir":5,"_draft":6,"_partial":6,"_locale":5,"title":7,"description":8,"visible":9